{"tid":87209,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Mozilla換咗新Logo　　你又發唔發現到？","createTime":"2017-01-19T15:28:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T05:34:08.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"32d7497f7a360931525d83bb9f80c860b7abe9c8","tid":87209,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T15:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/mozilla-typotheque-new-logo-2017.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2Fmozilla-typotheque-new-logo-2017.jpg&h=d1fbb7f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n未知大家有否發現，Mozilla的logo其實在多年來都沒有大改變。不過，由2017年起，他們正式換上新logo。和不少大公司一樣，Mozilla新logo也是採用簡約風格，使用獨特但又開源的Typotheque字體設計。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/mozilla-new-logo-2017.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2Fmozilla-new-logo-2017.jpg&h=a2e5b894&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新logo最明顯的分別，是當中的ill變成://，Mozilla表示這代表他們為完全開放、無過濾的互聯網做努力。Mozilla同時也推出一系列的設計手冊，允許網民做不同的設計，加上有趣的顏色或代表互聯網的圖案。<br />\n<br />\nMozilla launches new brand identity<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MuLWXHgyEVw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMuLWXHgyEVw&d=84eQHd2i79vBtAkCGwBTQ4scwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=97aa8770\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MuLWXHgyEVw</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2017/01/mozilla-new-logo-2017/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2017%2F01%2Fmozilla-new-logo-2017%2F&d=84eQHd2i79vBtAkCGwBTQ4scwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=e8047535\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2017/01/mozilla-new-logo-2017/</a>"},{"pid":"723d784bfe8919c1b44c472516a3691dc1e79344","tid":87209,"uid":61249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-2